ion to the collapse of Baltimore&#39;s Francis Scott Key Bridge, Synergy Marine Pte Ltd and Synergy Maritime Pte Ltd and one of its managers, have been charged with misconduct and obstruction. NBC News&#39; Tom Costello reports on details of the indictment in connection with the collision that killed six people.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778596979518_now_brk_bridge_charges_260512.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778596979518_now_brk_bridge_charges_260512.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778596979518_now_brk_bridge_charges_260512_S3_1920x1080-iuwfz5.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 14:43:07 GMT</pubDate><title>Ship operators involved in Baltimore bridge collapse charged with misconduct</title><updateDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 14:44:04 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>David Ingram</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 12 May 2026 16:10:04 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Altman is defending himself against Musk’s claims that he’s trying to enrich himself at the expense of OpenAI’s original nonprofit mission. </description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/sam-altman-takes-stand-defend-openai-elon-musk-claims-rcna344698</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/sam-altman-takes-stand-defend-openai-elon-musk-claims-rcna344698</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-openai-sam-altman-mn-1505-e8cb9e.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1201" width="1800"><media:credit>Benjamin Fanjoy</media:credit><media:text type="plain">OpenAI CEO Sam Altman in elevator</media:text><media:description type="plain">OpenAI CEO Sam Altman arrives at federal court on April 30 in Oakland, Calif. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260512-elon-musk-mn-0925-776164.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Godofredo A. Vásquez</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Elon Musk</media:text><media:description type="plain">OpenAI CEO Sam Altman arrives at federal court on April 30 in Oakland, Calif. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-openai-sam-altman-mn-1505-e8cb9e.jpg" height="1201" width="1800"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 16:10:04 GMT</pubDate><title>Sam Altman testifies in trial that Elon Musk ‘tried to kill’ OpenAI twice</title><updateDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 16:10:04 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Alexandra Marquez</dc:creator><dc:creator>Bridget Bowman</dc:creator><dc:creator>Ben Kamisar</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 12 May 2026 09:00:42 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Tuesday’s primary elections in Nebraska will set the stage for November in a battleground House district, as well as a potentially competitive Senate contest, as Democrats try to win control of Congress.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/nebraska-west-virginia-primaries-midterms-2026-house-senate-elections-rcna344471</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/nebraska-west-virginia-primaries-midterms-2026-house-senate-elections-rcna344471</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2025-07/250703-don-bacon-se-428p-e78b66.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Frank Thorp V</media:credit><media:text type="plain">“There’s some things I wish were better,” Bacon said. “But am I going to vote to raise taxes on middle-class Americans? I’m not.”</media:text><media:description type="plain">Retiring Republican Rep. Don Bacon&#39;s Nebraska district will be a key battleground for both parties in the fight for the House majority. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-02/260213-John-Cavanaugh-ew-212p-021dea.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Alex Wroblewski</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Nebraska Democratic State Senator John Cavanaugh</media:text><media:description type="plain">Retiring Republican Rep. Don Bacon&#39;s Nebraska district will be a key battleground for both parties in the fight for the House majority. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260511-denise-powell-for-congress-vl-346p-2d55d2.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1366" width="2048"><media:credit>Denise Powell for Congress</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Denise Powell stands inside of a room smiling with her arms cross</media:text><media:description type="plain">Retiring Republican Rep. Don Bacon&#39;s Nebraska district will be a key battleground for both parties in the fight for the House majority. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260511-cindy-burbank-william-forbes-nebraska-mb-1126-25b126.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="800" width="1200"><media:credit>cindyburbank.com; forbesfornebraska</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Cindy Burbank and William Forbes are facing off in Nebraska&#39;s Democratic Senate primary. </media:text><media:description type="plain">Retiring Republican Rep. Don Bacon&#39;s Nebraska district will be a key battleground for both parties in the fight for the House majority. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2024-01/240130-Shelley-Moore-Capito-se-1129a-59c2ff.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Drew Angerer</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Sen. Shelley Moore Capito, R-W.V., speaks during a news conference </media:text><media:description type="plain">Retiring Republican Rep. Don Bacon&#39;s Nebraska district will be a key battleground for both parties in the fight for the House majority. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2025-07/250703-don-bacon-se-428p-e78b66.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 09:00:42 GMT</pubDate><title>Tuesday’s primaries to set up key fall matchups in Nebraska</title><updateDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 09:00:42 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 12 May 2026 11:21:38 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Jake Rosmarin, one of the American passengers on the Hantavirus-stricken cruise ship, joins TODAY to speak out on entering quarantine at a hospital in Nebraska and recalls being stuck on the boat during the deadly outbreak. “It was definitely a wave of emotions as we retrieved information and I think it became more scary when we found out that Cape Verde authorities weren’t allowing us to dock,” he says.</description><expires>2056-05-12T11:20:55.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_7a_jake_rosmarin_hantavirus_passenger_260512</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/quarantined-passenger-talks-experience-on-hantavirus-hit-cruise-263150661684</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_7a_jake_rosmarin_hantavirus_passenger_260512/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Quarantined Passenger Talks Experience on Hantavirus-Hit Cruise</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/quarantined-passenger-talks-experience-on-hantavirus-hit-cruise-263150661684"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778584843037_tdy_news_7a_jake_rosmarin_hantavirus_passenger_260512_S3_1920x1080-a2pyvk.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">Jake Rosmarin, one of the American passengers on the Hantavirus-stricken cruise ship, joins TODAY to speak out on entering quarantine at a hospital in Nebraska and recalls being stuck on the boat during the deadly outbreak. “It was definitely a wave of emotions as we retrieved information and I think it became more scary when we found out that Cape Verde authorities weren’t allowing us to dock,” he says.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778584843037_tdy_news_7a_jake_rosmarin_hantavirus_passenger_260512.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778584843037_tdy_news_7a_jake_rosmarin_hantavirus_passenger_260512.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778584843037_tdy_news_7a_jake_rosmarin_hantavirus_passenger_260512_S3_1920x1080-a2pyvk.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 11:20:52 GMT</pubDate><title>Quarantined Passenger Talks Experience on Hantavirus-Hit Cruise</title><updateDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 11:21:38 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:52:01 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Speaking to reporters as he left the White House for his trip to China this afternoon, President Trump laid out his plan to discuss the Iran war with Chinese President Xi Jinping.</description><expires>2056-05